INSERT INTO
    vms_positions (
    call_sign,course,gross_tonnage,latitude,longitude,message_id,message_type,message_type_code,registration_id,speed,timestamp,vessel_length,vessel_name,vessel_type
   )
SELECT
    *
FROM
    UNNEST(
        $1::TEXT[],$2::INT[],$3::INT[],$4::DECIMAL[],$5::DECIMAL[],$6::INT[],$7::TEXT[],$8::TEXT[],$9::TEXT[],$10::DECIMAL[],$11::TIMESTAMPTZ[],$12::DECIMAL[],$13::TEXT[],$14::TEXT[]
    )
        ON CONFLICT (message_id,call_sign) DO NOTHING
